            "config": {
              "id": "QUE59165",
              "question": "During his first year of high school, Stan and his family move to the suburbs. At first, Stan has trouble fitting in and making friends, but by the time his first semester is over, he has a close-knit group of buddies. Stan’s friends smoke marijuana, and soon he begins to smoke it as well. How would the theory of differential association explain Stan’s behavior?\n\u003cbr /\u003e",
